Marilú Elízaga https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maril%C3%BA_El%C3%ADzaga 0 María Luisa Pérez-Caballero Moltó (1923–1995), commonly known by her stage name Marilú Elízaga, was a Spanish actress of theatre, television, and film. In 1958, she was nominated for an Ariel Award for Best Actress for the film La culta dama, directed by Rogelio A. González.
